{"lemma":"أَنَفَةٌ","slug":"أَنَفَةٌ","root":"#.ن.ف","root_slug":"_-ن-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ن-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1357","n1368"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَنِفَ (ʔanifa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conceitedness, disdain, haughtiness, vanity"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of أَنِفَ (ʔanifa)."},"ipa":["/ʔa.na.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1357","headword_ar":"اَنَفَهُ","root":"Anf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofN","text_ar":"اَنْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K;) namely, a man's. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the water)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reached his nose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K,) on the occasion of his descending into a river; (S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=nfhu","text_ar":"ا=نفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, [but in some copies written again"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anafahu","text_ar":"اَنَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iynaAfN","text_ar":"اـِينَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TK.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anafati AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"اَنَفَتِ الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n. as above, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels trod herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^unuf","text_ar":"اُنُف"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, S, K,) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which had not been pastured upon."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) [But in the TT, as from the M, I find ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=Anafa","text_ar":"ا=انَفَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (which should rather be written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aAnafa","text_ar":"اَانَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, accord. to the more usual mode,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=nafa","text_ar":"ا=نَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He trod such herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifa","text_ar":"اَنِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anafN","text_ar":"اَنَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a complaint of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suffered pain in, his nose, from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burap","text_ar":"بُرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nose-ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, M, K:) from ISk. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifati AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"اَنِفَتِ الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to certain of the Kilábees, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The flies alighted upon the noses of the camels, and they sought places which they did not seek before."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifa minohu","text_ar":"اَنِفَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anafN","text_ar":"اَنَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anafapN","text_ar":"اَنَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) or the latter is a simple subst., (Msb,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He turned up his nose at it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he disdained it; scorned it; abstained from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refused to do it, by reason of disdain and pride;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he disliked it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hated it, and his soul was above it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) namely, a thing: (S, M, L, Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he shunned it, avoided it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept himself far from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he disliked it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hated it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a saying. (AZ, T, Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAraA^ayotu A^aHomaY A^anafFA mino fulaAnK","text_ar":"مَارَاَيْتُ اَحْمَى اَنَفًا مِنْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen any one more vehemently disdainful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scornful, than such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala mino *`lika A^anafFA","text_ar":"حَمَلَ مِنْ ذٰلِكَ اَنَفًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He conceived, in consequence of that, disdain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scorn, arising from indignation and anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) [The verb is also trans. without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"text","text":": you say,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA^onafu A^ano yuDAma","text_ar":"يَاْنَفُ اَنْ يُضامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disdains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scorns,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refuses to bear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to submit to, being injured"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) [When immediately trans.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifa","text_ar":"اَنِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He loathed, disliked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded with disgust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifa AlbaEiyru AlkalaA^a","text_ar":"اَنِفَ البَعِيرُ الكَلَاَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camel loathed, disliked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded with disgust, the herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anfa AlT~aEaAma wagayorahu","text_ar":"اَنفَ الطَّعَامَ وَغَيْرَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disliked the food"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifato farasiY","text_ar":"اَنِفَتْ فَرَسِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi h`*aA Albalada","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ هٰذَا البَلَدَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This my mare disliked this region."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, as heard from an Arab of the desert.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^onafu faHolahaA","text_ar":"تَاْنَفُ فَحْلَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman, and a mare, and a camel, being pregnant,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dislikes her male,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stallion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifato","text_ar":"اَنِفَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a woman, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She, being pregnant, had no appetite for anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Abbád, K.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","K","ISk","Msb","L"]},{"entry_id":"n1368","headword_ar":"اَنَفَةٌ","root":"Anf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disdain; scorn; disdainful and proud incompliance or refusal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indignation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) a subst. [or, accord. to the S and M and K, an inf. n.] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anifa minohu","text_ar":"اَنِفَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}